name: Unknown entity
description: The entry needs an entity assigning before it will appear in the data.

name: Combined values
description: The field value has been constructed by combining data from multiple different entries.

name: Invalid coordinates
description: It was not possible to process the field as geospatial coordinates.

name: Invalid date
description: It was not possible to process the field as a date value.

name: Invalid decimal
description: It was not possible to process the field as a decimal number.

name: Invalid integer
description: It was not possible to process the field as an integer value.

name: Value too small
description: The number was less than the minimum value allowed for the field.

name: Value too large
description: The decimal value was greater than the maximum value allowed for the field.

name: Invalid flag
description: It was not possible to process the field as a yes or no value.

name: Invalid URI
description: It was not possible to process the field as a URI.

name: Invalid WKT
description: It was not possible to process the field as a WKT value.

name: Future entry date
description: The entry-date cannot be in the future.

name: Default field
description: The value has been taken from another field.

name: Default value
description: The value has been derived from other data.

name: Patched value
description: The value has changed during processing as a result of a patching rule in configuration.

name: WGS84 flipped
description: The latitude and longitude fields values have been exchanged.

name: WGS84 out of bounds
description: The geospatial coordinates are out of bounds.

name: Mercator conversion
description: The geospatial data has been processed as Mercator coordinates.

name: Mercator flipped
description: The geospatial data has been processed as flipped Mercator coordinates.

name: OSGB conversion
description: The geospatial data has been processed as OSGB coordinates.

name: OSGB flipped
description: The latitude and longitude fields have been processed as flipped OSGB coordinates.

name: Removed URI prefix
description: The URI value has been converted into a CURIE value.

name: Invalid geometry
description: An error encountered while processing the geometry has been resolved.

name: Invalid geometry
description: An error encountered while processing the geometry remains unresolved.

name: Invalid Organisation
description: Organisation data obtained during processing is invalid.

name: Unexpected Geometry Type
description: check the geometry type of a wkt if it's not within a given set and we remove it form the data.

name: Unexpected geom type within GeometryCollection
description: when a geometry collection is provided we check for a polygon if it doesn't exist then it is removed.

issue-type: WGS84 out of bounds of England
name: WGS84 out of bounds of England
description: Our default bounds are a bounding box around england. This issue is recorded when the geometry is outside of this.

issue-type: WGS84 out of bounds of custom boundary
name: WGS84 out of bounds of England
description: Our default bounds are a bounding box around england. This issue is recorded when the geometry is outside of this.

issue-type: OSGB out of bounds of England
name: OSGB out of bounds of England
description: Our default bounds are a bounding box around england. This issue is recorded when the geometry is outside of this.

issue-type: OSGB out of bounds of custom boundary
name: OSGB out of bounds of England
description: Our default bounds are a bounding box around england. This issue is recorded when the geometry is outside of this.

name: invalid Type Geojson
description: if reading a wkt fails this checks incase it can load a geojson.

name: Missing Value
description: This field is required in the dataset and while the field is in the resource the value is blank for the entry in the resource.

name: Unknown entity
description: The entry has a missing reference because of which entity cannot be assigned.

name: Reference values are not unique
description: There are multiple entries in this resource with this reference and entry date.
